    "content": "---\nname: documentation\ndescription: Write or improve concise product documentation for Staycation in Markdown. Use when the user wants to document a feature, product area, internal process, or functional behavior for business, marketing, tech, or other stakeholders.\n---\n\n# Product Documentation\n\nCreate factual, concise product documentation that answers the main reader questions without unnecessary storytelling.\n\n## Workflow\n\n1. Infer the right document scope from the request.\n2. Propose a logical Markdown filename when useful.\n3. Structure the content so it answers:\n   - What is it for\n   - Who is it for\n   - How does it work\n   - What business or product impact does it have\n4. Adapt the structure when the topic is more technical or more operational.\n\n## Default structure\n\n```md\n# [Feature or product area]\n\n## Objectif\n\n## Fonctionnement\n\n## Cas d'usage\n\n## Impact business / produit\n\n## Questions fréquentes\n```\n\n## Style\n\n- Keep paragraphs short.\n- Prefer factual language over storytelling.\n- Avoid unexplained jargon.\n- Optimize for mixed audiences across product, business, marketing, and tech."
